  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Motus GI is developing a single-use device that attaches to a standard colonoscope, thereby
      integrating colon cleansing, screening and treatment into one procedure. The device creates
      turbulence within the colon using water jets. The colon's fecal fluids are evacuated by the
      system.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
